{
  "video_id": "gtpTd3ywwiE",
  "title": "Martin Villeneuve: How I made an impossible film",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Joseph Geni Reviewer: Morton Bast"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 13670.0,
      "end_time": 15952.0,
      "text": "I made a film that was impossible to make,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 15952.0,
      "end_time": 19603.0,
      "text": "but I didn&#39;t know it was impossible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19603.0,
      "end_time": 22395.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s how I was able to do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22395.0,
      "end_time": 24855.0,
      "text": "\"Mars et Avril\" is a science fiction film."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 24855.0,
      "end_time": 29530.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s set in Montreal some 50 years in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29530.0,
      "end_time": 31255.0,
      "text": "No one had done that kind of movie in Quebec before"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31255.0,
      "end_time": 34937.0,
      "text": "because it&#39;s expensive, it&#39;s set in the future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34937.0,
      "end_time": 36596.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s got tons of visual effects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36597.0,
      "end_time": 39280.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s shot on green screen."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 39280.0,
      "end_time": 41179.0,
      "text": "Yet this is the kind of movie that I wanted to make"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 41179.0,
      "end_time": 43164.0,
      "text": "ever since I was a kid, really,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 43164.0,
      "end_time": 45273.0,
      "text": "back when I was reading some comic books"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 45273.0,
      "end_time": 48869.0,
      "text": "and dreaming about what the future might be."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 48869.0,
      "end_time": 51505.0,
      "text": "When American producers see my film,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 51505.0,
      "end_time": 54789.0,
      "text": "they think that I had a big budget to do it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 54789.0,
      "end_time": 57908.0,
      "text": "like 23 million."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 57908.0,
      "end_time": 60894.0,
      "text": "But in fact I had 10 percent of that budget."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 60894.0,
      "end_time": 63443.0,
      "text": "I did \"Mars et Avril\" for only 2.3 million."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 63443.0,
      "end_time": 64539.0,
      "text": "So you might wonder, what&#39;s the deal here?"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 64539.0,
      "end_time": 67920.0,
      "text": "How did I do this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 67920.0,
      "end_time": 70329.0,
      "text": "Well, it&#39;s two things. First, it&#39;s time."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 70329.0,
      "end_time": 73110.0,
      "text": "When you don&#39;t have money, you must take time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 73110.0,
      "end_time": 77200.0,
      "text": "and it took me seven years to do \"Mars et Avril.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 77200.0,
      "end_time": 80332.0,
      "text": "The second aspect is love."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 80332.0,
      "end_time": 83869.0,
      "text": "I got tons and tons of generosity from everyone involved."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 83870.0,
      "end_time": 86400.0,
      "text": "And it seems like every department had nothing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 86400.0,
      "end_time": 89680.0,
      "text": "so they had to rely on our creativity"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 89680.0,
      "end_time": 91642.0,
      "text": "and turn every problem into an opportunity."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 91642.0,
      "end_time": 93667.0,
      "text": "And that brings me to the point of my talk, actually,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 93668.0,
      "end_time": 97808.0,
      "text": "how constraints, big creative constraints, can boost creativity."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 97808.0,
      "end_time": 101216.0,
      "text": "But let me go back in time a bit."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 101216.0,
      "end_time": 104372.0,
      "text": "In my early 20s, I did some graphic novels,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 104373.0,
      "end_time": 106407.0,
      "text": "but they weren&#39;t your usual graphic novels."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 106407.0,
      "end_time": 108899.0,
      "text": "They were books telling a science fiction story"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 108900.0,
      "end_time": 111605.0,
      "text": "through images and text,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 111605.0,
      "end_time": 115188.0,
      "text": "and most of the actors who are now starring"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 115188.0,
      "end_time": 117246.0,
      "text": "in the movie adaptation, they were already involved"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 117246.0,
      "end_time": 120839.0,
      "text": "in these books portraying characters"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 120840.0,
      "end_time": 126387.0,
      "text": "into a sort of experimental, theatrical, simplistic way."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 126387.0,
      "end_time": 130900.0,
      "text": "And one of these actors is the great stage director"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 130900.0,
      "end_time": 131534.0,
      "text": "and actor Robert Lepage."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 131534.0,
      "end_time": 133540.0,
      "text": "And I just love this guy."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 133550.0,
      "end_time": 136500.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been in love with this guy since I was a kid."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 136500.0,
      "end_time": 139303.0,
      "text": "His career I admire a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 139303.0,
      "end_time": 142236.0,
      "text": "And I wanted this guy to be involved in my crazy project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 142236.0,
      "end_time": 146396.0,
      "text": "and he was kind enough to lend his image"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 146396.0,
      "end_time": 148590.0,
      "text": "to the character of Eugène Spaak,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 148590.0,
      "end_time": 152680.0,
      "text": "who is a cosmologist and artist who seeks relation"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 152681.0,
      "end_time": 158151.0,
      "text": "in between time, space, love, music and women."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 158151.0,
      "end_time": 161706.0,
      "text": "And he was a perfect fit for the part,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 161706.0,
      "end_time": 164890.0,
      "text": "and Robert is actually the one who gave me my first chance."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 164890.0,
      "end_time": 167226.0,
      "text": "He was the one who believed in me"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 167226.0,
      "end_time": 170803.0,
      "text": "and encouraged me to do an adaptation of my books"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 170803.0,
      "end_time": 173758.0,
      "text": "into a film, and to write, direct,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 173758.0,
      "end_time": 175810.0,
      "text": "and produce the film myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 175810.0,
      "end_time": 179620.0,
      "text": "And Robert is actually the very first example"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 179620.0,
      "end_time": 183504.0,
      "text": "of how constraints can boost creativity."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 183504.0,
      "end_time": 186171.0,
      "text": "Because this guy is the busiest man on the planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 186171.0,
      "end_time": 189293.0,
      "text": "I mean, his agenda is booked until 2042,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 189294.0,
      "end_time": 193134.0,
      "text": "and he&#39;s really hard to get,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 193134.0,
      "end_time": 196170.0,
      "text": "and I wanted him to be in the movie,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 196170.0,
      "end_time": 197922.0,
      "text": "to reprise his role in the movie."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 197922.0,
      "end_time": 200918.0,
      "text": "But the thing is, had I waited"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 200918.0,
      "end_time": 203470.0,
      "text": "for him until 2042, my film wouldn&#39;t be"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 203470.0,
      "end_time": 207266.0,
      "text": "a futuristic film anymore, so I just couldn&#39;t do that. Right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 207266.0,
      "end_time": 208950.0,
      "text": "But that&#39;s kind of a big problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 208950.0,
      "end_time": 212243.0,
      "text": "How do you get somebody who is too busy"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 212243.0,
      "end_time": 214369.0,
      "text": "to star in a movie?"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 214369.0,
      "end_time": 218271.0,
      "text": "Well, I said as a joke in a production meeting --"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 218271.0,
      "end_time": 220160.0,
      "text": "and this is a true story, by the way —"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 220160.0,
      "end_time": 222928.0,
      "text": "I said, \"Why don&#39;t we turn this guy into a hologram?"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 222928.0,
      "end_time": 225910.0,
      "text": "Because, you know, he is everywhere"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 225910.0,
      "end_time": 226957.0,
      "text": "and nowhere on the planet at the same time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 226957.0,
      "end_time": 229528.0,
      "text": "and he&#39;s an illuminated being in my mind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 229528.0,
      "end_time": 233781.0,
      "text": "and he&#39;s in between reality and virtual reality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 233782.0,
      "end_time": 235756.0,
      "text": "so it would make perfect sense"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 235756.0,
      "end_time": 238600.0,
      "text": "to turn this guy into a hologram.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 238600.0,
      "end_time": 240326.0,
      "text": "Everybody around the table laughed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 240326.0,
      "end_time": 242862.0,
      "text": "but the joke was kind of a good solution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 242862.0,
      "end_time": 245317.0,
      "text": "so that&#39;s what we ended up doing."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 245318.0,
      "end_time": 249210.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s how we did it. We shot Robert with six cameras."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 249210.0,
      "end_time": 251463.0,
      "text": "He was dressed in green and he was like"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 251463.0,
      "end_time": 253207.0,
      "text": "in a green aquarium."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 253207.0,
      "end_time": 255984.0,
      "text": "Each camera was covering 60 degrees of his head,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 255985.0,
      "end_time": 258598.0,
      "text": "so that in post-production we could use"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 258598.0,
      "end_time": 260490.0,
      "text": "pretty much any angle we needed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 260490.0,
      "end_time": 262902.0,
      "text": "and we shot only his head."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 262902.0,
      "end_time": 265407.0,
      "text": "Six months later there was a guy on set,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 265408.0,
      "end_time": 267238.0,
      "text": "a mime portraying the body,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 267238.0,
      "end_time": 269678.0,
      "text": "the vehicle for the head."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 269678.0,
      "end_time": 272929.0,
      "text": "And he was wearing a green hood"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 272929.0,
      "end_time": 276111.0,
      "text": "so that we could erase the green hood in postproduction"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 276111.0,
      "end_time": 278397.0,
      "text": "and replace it with Robert Lepage&#39;s head."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 278398.0,
      "end_time": 280406.0,
      "text": "So he became like a renaissance man,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 280406.0,
      "end_time": 282456.0,
      "text": "and here&#39;s what it looks like in the movie."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 282456.0,
      "end_time": 294776.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 294776.0,
      "end_time": 296944.0,
      "text": "(Video) Robert Lepage: [As usual, Arthur&#39;s drawing"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 296944.0,
      "end_time": 299138.0,
      "text": "didn&#39;t account for the technical challenges."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 299138.0,
      "end_time": 303800.0,
      "text": "I welded the breech, but the valve is still gaping."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 303810.0,
      "end_time": 307364.0,
      "text": "I tried to lift the pallets to lower the pressure in the sound box,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 307364.0,
      "end_time": 311296.0,
      "text": "but I might have hit a heartstring."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 311296.0,
      "end_time": 313678.0,
      "text": "It still sounds too low.]"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 313678.0,
      "end_time": 314609.0,
      "text": "Jacques Languirand: [That&#39;s normal."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 314609.0,
      "end_time": 317770.0,
      "text": "The instrument always ends up resembling its model.]"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 317771.0,
      "end_time": 323301.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 338266.0,
      "end_time": 341684.0,
      "text": "Martin Villeneuve: Now these musical instruments"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 341684.0,
      "end_time": 343828.0,
      "text": "that you see in this excerpt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 343828.0,
      "end_time": 346335.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re my second example of how"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 346335.0,
      "end_time": 348727.0,
      "text": "constraints can boost creativity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 348727.0,
      "end_time": 351947.0,
      "text": "because I desperately needed these objects in my movie."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 351947.0,
      "end_time": 353648.0,
      "text": "They are objects of desire."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 353648.0,
      "end_time": 356430.0,
      "text": "They are imaginary musical instruments."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 356430.0,
      "end_time": 358123.0,
      "text": "And they carry a nice story with them."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 358123.0,
      "end_time": 362777.0,
      "text": "Actually, I knew what these things would look like"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 362777.0,
      "end_time": 364607.0,
      "text": "in my mind for many, many years."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 364607.0,
      "end_time": 368820.0,
      "text": "But my problem was, I didn&#39;t have the money"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 368820.0,
      "end_time": 371601.0,
      "text": "to pay for them. I couldn&#39;t afford them."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 371601.0,
      "end_time": 374320.0,
      "text": "So that&#39;s kind of a big problem too."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 374320.0,
      "end_time": 377633.0,
      "text": "How do you get something that you can&#39;t afford?"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 377633.0,
      "end_time": 381592.0,
      "text": "And, you know, I woke up one morning with a pretty good idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 381593.0,
      "end_time": 385756.0,
      "text": "I said, \"What if I have somebody else pay for them?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 385756.0,
      "end_time": 388616.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 388617.0,
      "end_time": 392345.0,
      "text": "But who on Earth would be interested"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 392345.0,
      "end_time": 395561.0,
      "text": "by seven not-yet-built musical instruments"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 395561.0,
      "end_time": 397260.0,
      "text": "inspired by women&#39;s bodies?"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 397261.0,
      "end_time": 400175.0,
      "text": "And I thought of Cirque du Soleil in Montreal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 400175.0,
      "end_time": 403533.0,
      "text": "because who better to understand the kind of"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 403533.0,
      "end_time": 406212.0,
      "text": "crazy poetry that I wanted to put on screen?"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 406212.0,
      "end_time": 409385.0,
      "text": "So I found my way to Guy Laliberté, Cirque du Soleil&#39;s CEO,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 409386.0,
      "end_time": 412154.0,
      "text": "and I presented my crazy idea to him"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 412154.0,
      "end_time": 415388.0,
      "text": "with sketches like this and visual references,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 415388.0,
      "end_time": 418114.0,
      "text": "and something pretty amazing happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 418115.0,
      "end_time": 420466.0,
      "text": "Guy was interested by this idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 420466.0,
      "end_time": 423771.0,
      "text": "not because I was asking for his money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 423771.0,
      "end_time": 427197.0,
      "text": "but because I came to him with a good idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 427197.0,
      "end_time": 428919.0,
      "text": "in which everybody was happy."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 428919.0,
      "end_time": 431270.0,
      "text": "It was kind of a perfect triangle"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 431280.0,
      "end_time": 434515.0,
      "text": "in which the art buyer was happy"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 434515.0,
      "end_time": 437455.0,
      "text": "because he got the instruments at a cheaper price,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 437455.0,
      "end_time": 439328.0,
      "text": "because they weren&#39;t even made."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 439328.0,
      "end_time": 440936.0,
      "text": "He took a leap of faith."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 440937.0,
      "end_time": 444794.0,
      "text": "And the artist, Dominique Engel, brilliant guy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 444794.0,
      "end_time": 447623.0,
      "text": "he was happy too because he had a dream project"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 447623.0,
      "end_time": 449104.0,
      "text": "to work on for a year."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 449104.0,
      "end_time": 452918.0,
      "text": "And obviously I was happy because I got the instruments"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 452918.0,
      "end_time": 457726.0,
      "text": "in my film for free, which was kind of what I tried to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 457726.0,
      "end_time": 459444.0,
      "text": "So here they are."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 459444.0,
      "end_time": 462918.0,
      "text": "And my last example of how constraints"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 462918.0,
      "end_time": 464427.0,
      "text": "can boost creativity"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 464427.0,
      "end_time": 468370.0,
      "text": "comes from the green,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 468370.0,
      "end_time": 471880.0,
      "text": "because this is a weird color, a crazy color,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 471880.0,
      "end_time": 474942.0,
      "text": "and you need to replace the green screens eventually"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 474942.0,
      "end_time": 477763.0,
      "text": "and you must figure that out sooner rather than later."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 477763.0,
      "end_time": 481936.0,
      "text": "And I had, again, pretty much, ideas in my mind"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 481936.0,
      "end_time": 483952.0,
      "text": "as to what the world would be,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 483952.0,
      "end_time": 489300.0,
      "text": "but then again I turned to my childhood imagination"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 489300.0,
      "end_time": 492592.0,
      "text": "and went to the work of Belgian comic book master"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 492593.0,
      "end_time": 495241.0,
      "text": "François Schuiten in Belgium."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 495241.0,
      "end_time": 498561.0,
      "text": "And this guy is another guy I admire a lot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 498561.0,
      "end_time": 501320.0,
      "text": "and I wanted him to be involved in the movie"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 501330.0,
      "end_time": 503281.0,
      "text": "as a production designer."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 503281.0,
      "end_time": 505618.0,
      "text": "But people told me, you know, Martin, it&#39;s impossible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 505618.0,
      "end_time": 508305.0,
      "text": "the guy is too busy and he will say no."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 508305.0,
      "end_time": 512159.0,
      "text": "Well, I said, you know what, instead of mimicking his style,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 512159.0,
      "end_time": 514158.0,
      "text": "I might as well call the real guy and ask him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 514158.0,
      "end_time": 516834.0,
      "text": "and I sent him my books,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 516832.99999999994,
      "end_time": 518856.99999999994,
      "text": "and he answered that he was interested"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 518857.0,
      "end_time": 520678.0,
      "text": "in working on the film with me"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 520678.0,
      "end_time": 524862.0,
      "text": "because he could be a big fish in a small aquarium."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 524862.0,
      "end_time": 528756.0,
      "text": "In other words, there was space for him to dream with me."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 528756.0,
      "end_time": 531589.0,
      "text": "So here I was with one of my childhood heroes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 531590.0,
      "end_time": 534535.0,
      "text": "drawing every single frame that&#39;s in the film"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 534535.0,
      "end_time": 537749.0,
      "text": "to turn that into Montreal in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 537749.0,
      "end_time": 539873.0,
      "text": "And it was an amazing collaboration"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 539873.0,
      "end_time": 542526.0,
      "text": "to work with this great artist whom I admire."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 542526.0,
      "end_time": 546214.0,
      "text": "But then, you know, eventually you have to turn"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 546214.0,
      "end_time": 548238.0,
      "text": "all these drawings into reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 548238.0,
      "end_time": 551367.0,
      "text": "So, again, my solution was to aim"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 551367.0,
      "end_time": 554473.0,
      "text": "for the best possible artist that I could think of."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 554474.0,
      "end_time": 557875.0,
      "text": "And there&#39;s this guy in Montreal, another Quebecois"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 557875.0,
      "end_time": 561857.0,
      "text": "called Carlos Monzon, and he&#39;s a very good VFX artist."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 561857.0,
      "end_time": 565339.0,
      "text": "This guy had been lead compositor on such films"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 565339.0,
      "end_time": 568286.0,
      "text": "as \"Avatar\" and \"Star Trek\" and \"Transformers,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 568286.0,
      "end_time": 570518.0,
      "text": "and other unknown projects like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 570519.0,
      "end_time": 573433.0,
      "text": "and I knew he was the perfect fit for the job,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 573433.0,
      "end_time": 574976.0,
      "text": "and I had to convince him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 574976.0,
      "end_time": 578407.0,
      "text": "and, instead of working on the next Spielberg movie,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 578407.0,
      "end_time": 580463.0,
      "text": "he accepted to work on mine."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 580463.0,
      "end_time": 584250.0,
      "text": "Why? Because I offered him a space to dream."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 584250.0,
      "end_time": 587664.0,
      "text": "So if you don&#39;t have money to offer to people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 587664.0,
      "end_time": 590879.0,
      "text": "you must strike their imagination with something"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 590879.0,
      "end_time": 593391.0,
      "text": "as nice as you can think of."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 593391.0,
      "end_time": 595766.0,
      "text": "So this is what happened on this movie,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 595767.0,
      "end_time": 597108.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s how it got made,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 597108.0,
      "end_time": 600238.0,
      "text": "and we went to this very nice postproduction company"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 600239.0,
      "end_time": 602311.0,
      "text": "in Montreal called Vision Globale,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 602311.0,
      "end_time": 606948.0,
      "text": "and they lent their 60 artists to work full time"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 606948.0,
      "end_time": 609894.0,
      "text": "for six months to do this crazy film."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 609894.0,
      "end_time": 614683.0,
      "text": "So I want to tell you that, if you have some crazy ideas"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 614683.0,
      "end_time": 616356.0,
      "text": "in your mind, and that people tell you"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 616356.0,
      "end_time": 617843.0,
      "text": "that it&#39;s impossible to make,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 617843.0,
      "end_time": 620438.0,
      "text": "well, that&#39;s an even better reason to want to do it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 620438.0,
      "end_time": 622538.0,
      "text": "because people have a tendency"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 622538.0,
      "end_time": 625869.0,
      "text": "to see the problems rather than the final result,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 625869.0,
      "end_time": 628651.0,
      "text": "whereas if you start to deal with problems"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 628651.0,
      "end_time": 631453.0,
      "text": "as being your allies rather than your opponents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 631453.0,
      "end_time": 633964.0,
      "text": "life will start to dance with you"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 633964.0,
      "end_time": 635520.0,
      "text": "in the most amazing way."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 635520.0,
      "end_time": 637208.0,
      "text": "I have experienced it."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 637208.0,
      "end_time": 640266.0,
      "text": "And you might end up doing some crazy projects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 640267.0,
      "end_time": 643206.0,
      "text": "and who knows, you might even end up"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 643206.0,
      "end_time": 645470.0,
      "text": "going to Mars."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 645470.0,
      "end_time": 647171.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 647171.0,
      "end_time": 650386.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}